{"_path":"/councilor/service/s4079","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"成功爭取 607 公車增班，預計4月上路！","description":null,"image":"/images/service/4079-1.jpeg","sequence":4079,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":null,"author":"陳雅倫","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"陳雅倫"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-03-14T00:00:00.000Z","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"成功爭取-607-公車增班預計-4-月上路"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"成功爭取 607 公車增班，預計 4 月上路！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經過多次努力爭取，607 公車增班終於獲得核准，預計於 4 月正式上路！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"過去，雅倫曾多次向相關單位反映，希望增加 607 公車的班次，以紓解通勤時段的擁擠情況，並提升服務品質。此次增班的成功，是所有乘客長期關注與支持的成果！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"此外，我也"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持續向相關單位提請評估增設「文青國中小」公車站"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，讓周邊居民及學童能有更便利的搭乘選擇。同時，也"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要求 603 公車同步增班"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，雙循環公車要上路，希望能夠進一步強化重劃區整體公車運輸網絡，這些我都會繼續努力 💪"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"未來，我將繼續關注公共交通議題，還有前兩年被裁減的萬壽路幹線公車、大迴龍公車、社區免巴，希望桃園變得更宜居、更便利！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4079-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4079-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"成功爭取-607-公車增班預計-4-月上路","depth":2,"text":"成功爭取 607 公車增班，預計 4 月上路！"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s4079.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s4079.md","_extension":"md"}